{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Assisted pull ups - 90 lbs 10, 80 lbs 10*, 10*\nLat pulldown - 87 lbs 10, 125 lbs 10, 187lbs>125lbs>75lbs 5>5**>5 slow...5 fast...1 hold 5 secs\nChest-supported rows - 75 lbs 10, 87 lbs 12, 99 lbs 10\nDb shrugs / Lat raise - 30 lbs/15 lbs 10/10, 10/12, 35lbs/15 lbs 15/12\nReverse pec deck fly - 60 lbs 10, 70 lbs 10, 10\nBarbell row - bar+2x25lbs 10, bar+2x(25lbs+5lbs) 12, bar+2x(25lbs+2x5lbs) 10**\nPreacher curls - 20 lbs 10, 40 lbs 10, 40lbs>20lbs 6>4\nForearm curls / reverse forearm curls - 15lbs/4kg 15/10, 15/12, 15/12\nFacepull - 70 lbs 10, 80 lbs 10***, 10***\nBicep curl - 15 lbs 10~10, 20lbs>15lbs 5~6>5>4, 5~5...2~2>3~3\n\nNotes:\n* - di ko na abot taas\n** - pagod sa dulo\n*** - had to take breaks by 7/8 reps \n\nWeight: 78.8 kg","title":"Nov 27, 2025","userEditedTimestampUsec":1764248004836000,"createdTimestampUsec":1764242442258000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Assisted pull ups - 90 lbs 10, 80 lbs 10*, 10*<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Lat pulldown - 87 lbs 10, 125 lbs 10, 187lbs&gt;125lbs&gt;75lbs 5&gt;5**&gt;5 slow...5 fast...1 hold 5 secs<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant